--------------------------------------------------
BUSINESS RULES
--------------------------------------------------

• Only Accepted Quotations may create Orders.

• One Accepted Quotation creates one Order.

• Customers may only access Orders belonging to their approved company.

• Every Order update creates a history record.

• Soft delete only where appropriate.

• Validate every status transition.

• Never trust IDs from the frontend.

• Prevent IDOR attacks.

• Use optimistic concurrency.

• Paginate all list APIs.

• Support filtering and searching.

• Use DTOs for all requests/responses.

